&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/10357&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/10357&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="83409" author="adilger" created="Wed, 7 May 2014 17:26:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m reopening this to track a patch to remove test_57b from ALWAYS_EXCEPT in conf-sanity.sh for ZFS.  This bug was closed as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2059&quot; title=&quot;mgc to backup configuration on osd-based llogs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2059&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2059&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but I think the main part of that bug has since been fixed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please submit a patch that removes 57b from ALWAYS_EXCEPT, and has a Test-parameters: line that runs conf-sanity maybe ten times to see how often it is passing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="52806" author="jlevi" created="Thu, 21 Feb 2013 10:41:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2059&quot; title=&quot;mgc to backup configuration on osd-based llogs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2059&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2059&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="52195" author="tappro" created="Tue, 12 Feb 2013 03:52:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;it should be fixed with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2059&quot; title=&quot;mgc to backup configuration on osd-based llogs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2059&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2059&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the problem is that mgc may have local configs if it is server node, but that code worked using lvfs that is not case for ZFS obviously. With patch from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2059&quot; title=&quot;mgc to backup configuration on osd-based llogs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2059&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2059&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; local configs code works via OSD API.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
